HTML Part 

top navbar - to be created in HTML 
colour icon div and add button and remove/close button 

on click Modal to add the note
Modal : 
1. Text Area 
2. Colour Selection Widget

Task Card : 
1. Top strip of color  
2. task description
3. lock icon
4. Unlock icon
5. Unique id strip 

Functionality :

Event Listener : 
1. Click Event on add button 
2. Click on the colour Widget
3. Keydown event on eter button 
4. Click event on the top strip of the task Card
5. Click event on Lock/Unlock button 
Click event on the remove button 
click event on the task card to remove
6. Click event on the top color icons
7. Double click evet on top color icons




Font Awesome : Used to add icons to our code. Icons are lightweight and do not add load of downloading images. Also, using icons in the code improves the performance of our website. 

